ets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食好多都有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通天閣可以唔駛去<br />\n巴打鍾意動漫嘢嘅可以去日本橋<br />\n可以google下信長書店，但記得千祈千祈唔好帶老母去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12593016de4a88251f9ec529ba6c6a892b8806f3","tid":115510,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得通天閣好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4653d73d2bbb1ddceead874071fff804f824f67c","tid":115510,"uid":78534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>心齋橋就一定要去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食好多都有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通天閣可以唔駛去<br />\n巴打鍾意動漫嘢嘅可以去日本橋<br />\n可以google下信長書店，但記得千祈千祈唔好帶老母去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇過下心齋橋都幾多人，賣既衫平時係香港都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我係sis黎，諗住9遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad94b0ce1d45c9070f05e43b4814d8df9dd7e826","tid":115510,"uid":22663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"去京都好過啦"},{"pid":"ba59b659e8f7926f365a933cf84bf798c368af4d","tid":115510,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去京都好過啦</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n起馬多d野睇<br />\n如果樓主老母鐘意風景同古蹟再講<br />\n<br />\n大阪去川之島魚市場燒下海鮮"},{"pid":"51ec09c7eda6ce3b7d6df80d16e5a904893585e4","tid":115510,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"萬博公園 睇完花又可以係隔離行商場食飯"},{"pid":"b5fabdba2b2f1604fff3461ecbf6578fb11e085f","tid":115510,"uid":32757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"搵一日去奈良撚下鹿 唔叫太遠 所以令母都應該唔會坐到腰痛<br />\n但講真既 要行街就留係香港行啦 去撚到日本都係行街就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早排先去完大阪 去完個人係放鬆左既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2827075a0673cb3b092df4464dde57b450c5ad","tid":115510,"uid":82131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"去京都睇下清水寺呀<br />\n雖然維修緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n銀閣金閣寺, 水族館咁"},{"pid":"15e16d5da14ecaabb31ef940b3fceef994473665","tid":115510,"uid":22902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"去埋奈良餵鹿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯係神戶個元町個d都幾好行<br />\n呢間好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/142958_07173a28cc8f2c17495cfa1eb704009a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://